      <title>日本首相将在领导人辩论中面临新的选举要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/japan-pm-set-to-face-new-calls-for-election-in-leaders-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄很可能将在他上任以来的首次政党领袖辩论中面临宣布举行大选的新一轮压力，而他的支持率目前正处于历史最低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/japan-pm-set-to-face-new-calls-for-election-in-leaders-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 00:38:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登邀请比尔·克林顿和希拉里·克林顿对抗特朗普的筹款活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/biden-taps-bill-clinton-hillary-clinton-to-fundraise-against-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，总统乔·拜登与前总统比尔·克林顿和前民主党总统候选人希拉里·克林顿一起出席了弗吉尼亚州的一场筹款活动，这是为期一周的疯狂筹款活动的一部分，旨在抵消前总统唐纳德·特朗普收到的大量捐款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/biden-taps-bill-clinton-hillary-clinton-to-fundraise-against-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 00:09:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔将于 6 月底逐步取消“不公平”汽油补贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/ecuador-to-phase-out-unfair-gasoline-subsidy-in-late-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔总统丹尼尔·诺沃亚一月份宣布对贩毒团伙宣战，厄瓜多尔政府于周二公布了一项大幅削减低辛烷值汽油补贴的计划，以继续调整公共财政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/ecuador-to-phase-out-unfair-gasoline-subsidy-in-late-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 21:26:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国钢铁公司首席执行官“非常有信心”新日铁交易将于 2024 年完成</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/us-steel-ceo-extremely-confident-nippon-deal-will-close-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国钢铁公司老板戴维·伯里特 (David Burritt) 坚信，尽管遭到工会领导人和拜登政府的强烈反对，新日铁 141 亿美元的收购案仍将在今年进行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/us-steel-ceo-extremely-confident-nippon-deal-will-close-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 21:14:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国、意大利等七个欧盟国家因赤字受到谴责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/france-italy-among-7-eu-nations-to-be-reprimanded-over-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，法国和意大利将成为因去年赤字过高而面临欧盟侵权程序的七个国家之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/france-italy-among-7-eu-nations-to-be-reprimanded-over-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 21:07:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>李克强总理访问马来西亚 安华平衡中美利益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/premier-li-visits-malaysia-as-anwar-balances-us-china-interests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国务院总理李强于周二晚间开始对马来西亚进行为期三天的访问，北京希望加深与马来西亚的关系，在中美竞争加剧的情况下，马来西亚一直保持中立。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/premier-li-visits-malaysia-as-anwar-balances-us-china-interests</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩 24 年来首次访朝，与普京拥抱致意</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/putin-arrives-in-north-korea-for-first-visit-in-24-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京 24 年来首次访问朝鲜，而美国则警告称，此次会晤可能会导致金正恩政权进一步向朝鲜转让武器，以帮助克里姆林宫攻打乌克兰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/putin-arrives-in-north-korea-for-first-visit-in-24-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 19:23:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司首席执行官因“安全记录不佳”遭参议员批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/boeing-ceo-under-fire-from-senators-for-broken-safety-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司首席执行官戴夫·卡尔霍恩在参议院听证会上受到严厉批评，批评主要集中在公司的制造缺陷上，并指责公司领导人将利润置于安全之上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/boeing-ceo-under-fire-from-senators-for-broken-safety-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 19:01:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍勃·梅内德斯在贿赂案审判中得到检察官的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/bob-menendez-gets-boost-at-bribery-trial-from-a-us-attorney</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新泽西州最高联邦检察官周二在参议员鲍勃·梅嫩德斯受贿案审判中似乎为其提供了帮助，他告诉陪审员，这位民主党议员从未向他施压，让他做任何不当行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/bob-menendez-gets-boost-at-bribery-trial-from-a-us-attorney</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 18:36:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡告诉美国‘给我们工具，我们将完成工作’</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/netanyahu-tells-us-give-us-the-tools-we-ll-finish-the-job</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡表示，总统乔·拜登在与哈马斯的战争中扣留武器，因为他的国家正在“为生存而战”，但白宫否认了这一指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/netanyahu-tells-us-give-us-the-tools-we-ll-finish-the-job</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:44:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
